0.5.name: wordpress/lap-leos-adsense
0.5.description: This plugin allows add AdSense code to your posts. Important is, that this plugin allows you to specify different ID and channel ID or ad-slot ID (Useful, if you have several authors of your pages with their own AdSense settings) for each post. All IDs are specified at each post separately. Plugin can identify how old is your post also and can show AdSense ads for posts older than days you specify.
